    "date": "2003-09-30T20:29:58Z",
    "text": "Homestead Preservation Act - Directs the Secretary of Labor to establish a program of low-interest loan (residential) mortgage assistance to eligible persons who are separated from their employment.\n\nLimits assistance to 12 months, and requires repayment within five years."
